  "detailed_description": "<h1>UltimateDesktop Collection</h1><p><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Software</h1>Ultimate Live Wallpaper is an amazing lightweight AAA live wallpaper engine with stunning 3D animation effects and mouse interaction.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Support Windows 10 / 8.1 / 8 / 7(with Aero)<br></li><li>Support Steam Workshop<br></li><li>Support Disable Steam In Preferences<br></li><li>Interactive action - react to mouse movements and clicks.<br></li><li>Many options - you can change almost every element in the wallpaper settings.<br></li><li>Game Mode - will pause wallpaper when you need 100% power for your games.<br></li><li>Optimization - reduced equipment requirements.  CPU usage as low as 1%</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FAQ</h2>Q: How to download VFX/Themes from Steam Workshop?<br>A: 1. Open theme manage window by click tray icon popup menu item \"Theme\", switch to \"Workshop\" page to Subscrib Workshop Theme Items.<br>    2. Open wallpaper setting window window by click tray icon popup menu item \"Wallpaper Setting\", Click Top-Right coner Download Button to open the Workshop window to Subscrib Workshop VFX Items.",
  "about_the_game": "Ultimate Live Wallpaper is an amazing lightweight AAA live wallpaper engine with stunning 3D animation effects and mouse interaction.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Support Windows 10 / 8.1 / 8 / 7(with Aero)<br></li><li>Support Steam Workshop<br></li><li>Support Disable Steam In Preferences<br></li><li>Interactive action - react to mouse movements and clicks.<br></li><li>Many options - you can change almost every element in the wallpaper settings.<br></li><li>Game Mode - will pause wallpaper when you need 100% power for your games.<br></li><li>Optimization - reduced equipment requirements.  CPU usage as low as 1%</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FAQ</h2>Q: How to download VFX/Themes from Steam Workshop?<br>A: 1. Open theme manage window by click tray icon popup menu item \"Theme\", switch to \"Workshop\" page to Subscrib Workshop Theme Items.<br>    2. Open wallpaper setting window window by click tray icon popup menu item \"Wallpaper Setting\", Click Top-Right coner Download Button to open the Workshop window to Subscrib Workshop VFX Items.",
